"{\"uid\": \"cnbc.com-2024-07-31-simone-biles-credits-therapy-for-her-success-at-the-paris-olympics.html\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Related Stories There is one thing that Simone Biles credits for her return to the Olympics this year: therapy.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 34}, {\"ngram\": \"her return\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 75}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 91}, {\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is now themost decorated U.S. Olympic gymnast in historywith eight Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. Olympic gymnast\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 167}, {\"ngram\": \"historywith\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"eight Olympic medals\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she says it would not have been possible without consistent mental health support.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"consistent mental health support\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being in a good mental spot, seeing my therapist every Thursday is kind of religious for me.\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good mental spot\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"my therapist\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"every Thursday\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So that's why I am here today,\\\" Biles said in aninterviewwith NBC News last month.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9913625527456154, \"rank\": 0.008618091543565201, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The road to victory wasn't an easy one for Biles.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The road\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"an easy one\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago,she withdrew from the team gymnastics competitionat the postponed 2020 Tokyo Olympics citing mental health concerns.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team gymnastics competitionat\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 588}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health concerns\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She later explained that she was experiencing what gymnasts refer to as \\\"the twisties.\\\"\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the twisties is not an official medical diagnosis, the experience is used to describe a psychologically-perceived disconnection between a gymnast's mind and their body as they are performing, especially during twists.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"an official medical diagnosis\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 817}, {\"ngram\": \"a psychologically-perceived disconnection\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"a gymnast's mind\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"their body\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"twists\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The effects of the twisties can range from missing twists or twisting more than one planned to, and landing or falling in a way that can cause injury.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The effects\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"missing twists\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Biles was completing an Amanar vault at the 2020 Olympics, she noticeably turned 1.5 twists instead of the usual 2.5.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1152, \"end\": 1158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8120384880063897e-40, \"text\": \"Amanar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"1.5 twists\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even onlookers noticed that sheseemed disoriented during the twist.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even onlookers\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the twist\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to focus on my mental health,\\\" Bilessaidafter pulling out of the Olympics in 2021.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not trust myself as much anymore.\\\"\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles regained that trust within herself by starting small through practicing on soft surfaces and in ball pits,she shared via Instagram.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 15